#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.62"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.62:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.62:0.2"
msgid "7. Paṭhamaāmakadhaññapeyyālavagga"
msgstr "7. Abbreviated Texts on Raw Grain"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.62:0.3"
msgid "62. Paccantasutta"
msgstr "62. In the Borderlands"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.62:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā parittaṃ nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsuṃ āropetvā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then the Buddha, picking up a little bit of dirt under his fingernail, "
"addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn56.62:1.2"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.62:1.3"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yo vāyaṃ mayā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito, "
"ayaṃ vā mahāpathavī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the little bit of dirt under my fingernail, or this great "
"earth?”"

msgctxt "sn56.62:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ, yadidaṃ—mahāpathavī; appamattakāyaṃ bhagavatā "
"paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the great earth is certainly more. The little bit of dirt under your "
"fingernail is tiny."

msgctxt "sn56.62:1.5"
msgid ""
"Saṅkhampi na upeti, upanidhampi na upeti, kalabhāgampi na upeti mahāpathaviṃ "
"upanidhāya bhagavatā paritto nakhasikhāyaṃ paṃsu āropito”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the great earth, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even "
"a fraction.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: milakkhesu → milakkhūsu (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "sn56.62:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appamattakā te sattā ye majjhimesu janapadesu "
"paccājāyanti; atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā ye paccantimesu janapadesu "
"paccājāyanti aviññātāresu milakkhesu … pe …."
msgstr ""
"“In the same way, the sentient beings reborn in central countries are few, "
"while those reborn in the borderlands, among barbarian tribes, are many. …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.62:2.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
